# Generated deployable site — `npm run build` assembles the full static app
# (bundles, minified core, all-in-one, runtime files, docs, demos, assets) into
# _site/ from docs/ + the root library sources. Built by the `prepare` hook on
# `npm install`; served with `npm run serve`; deployed via a GitHub Action.
/_site/
